# {{projectName}} Kubernetes Manifests

This pack provides Kubernetes base manifests and a starter Helm chart for {{projectName}}.

## Contents
- Namespace
- Deployment + Service + Ingress
- ConfigMap + Secret
- HPA, PDB, NetworkPolicy, ServiceAccount, RBAC
- Starter Helm chart (Chart.yaml, values.yaml, helpers)

## Usage

```bash
kubectl apply -f k8s/namespace.yaml
kubectl apply -f k8s/
```

Helm chart:

```bash
helm install {{kebabCase projectName}} ./helm -n {{kebabCase projectName}}
```

## Customization
- Set container image/tag in values.yaml and k8s/deployment.yaml.
- Adjust resources, env vars, and ingress hosts.